Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:08.82,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian youth, Lelouch, met the mysterious girl, C.C., and obtained a special power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:10.62,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:13.41,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to give an order to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:14.99,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,A power that enforces absolute obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:20.96,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of his sister, Nanali, Lelouch plans the destruction of the Imperial Britannian Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:27.74,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, his friend, Kururugi Suzaku, has found a place within the Imperial Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.11,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,At this point in time, the future they are about to embark upon has become the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:35.18,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Or you could say it has long been preordained.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.96,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time that I've gone out of the Tokyo settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:43.75,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been nice if Lelouch had come along though, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.37,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:49.73,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we agree that tonight we'd talk about the type of men we like until dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.94,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,President, do you have such a person...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.23,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:02:59.91,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.39,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of Britannian tourists in Kawaguchiko too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.44,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,The security is good there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.46,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,It's not scary, like the ghettos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.37,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.20,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.13,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,We won't leave you behind this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:13.04,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.59,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.29,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.47,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, this shall be our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.94,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I take it you're wiling to cooperate with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.06,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.21,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What is all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.35,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get such a thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.37,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,These corrupt aristocrats are willing to give me whatever I request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.48,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Request?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.78,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:48.92,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I covered my tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.48,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. There's a second story too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.09,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this vehicle a bit too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:56.96,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, they may not suspect a hideout this conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.72,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,There's a television in here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.38,Default,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything going on out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:01.38,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.49,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:05.37,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm reporting from in front of the Kawaguchiko Convention Center Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.14,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The hoteljackers claim to be from the Japanese Liberation Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:12.53,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,They have taken Chairman James, the members attending the conference on the division of Sakuradite,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:16.86,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,tourists who were around there and several staff members as hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.40,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,This is a video that the culprits sent to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.36,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Several students can be seen here along with Chairman James.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.40,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,The student council...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.32,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:29.83,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the criminal group calls himself Lieutenant Colonel Kusakabe, a former Japanese army soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.70,Default,Todo,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.87,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuradite, as it is essential in the manufacturing of high temperature super-conductive substance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:39.17,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,directly affects the national security of the world. It's an important war resource.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:43.20,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,This place, Area 11, is the world's largest production zone of Sakuradite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.80,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,It supplies up to 70% of the market's demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.35,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The National Sakuradite Conference is held here every year
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.12,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,in order to decide the ratio of Sakuradite each country is allotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:05:00.14,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The result is said to determine the power balance between Britannia and the other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:04.92,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The terrorists were probably aware of the international attention being placed on this conference
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.67,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,and have thus carried out this bold act of hoteljacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.17,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kusakabe of the Japanese Liberation Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.53,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,We have stood up for the independence of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.02,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, even though you aren't soldiers, are Britannians.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.84,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who rule over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:23.63,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Be obedient and all will be well, {\i1\b1\u1}or else!{\b0\i0\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.38,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.06,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,They've made their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.68,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,They are the biggest anti-Britannia faction in Japan after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.91,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they don't want to play second fiddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:31.96,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:32.83,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.57,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Should we rejoice or should we be sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.27,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What they're doing out there is suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.48,Note,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,While the staff acknowledges it definitely says "Rivalz" here, we would like to treat it as Engrish and stick to spelling it Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:38.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.36,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.99,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he doing at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:48.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:55.12,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,All of the bridges that link to the hotel have been destroyed, except for the main one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.87,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Attempts to approach via air and sea have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:03.59,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one route left for us to take if we wish to commence an operation to rescue the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.89,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The lifeline tunnel is directly under the convention center.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:14.35,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,If we used that in our operation, we can destroy the foundation block and sink the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:19.77,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,This tunnel is used to deliver stock, and thus, a Sutherland might be able to fit through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:22.61,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is most likely prepared, but there shouldn't be any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:25.57,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:29.53,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the level of weaponry that our opponents have used so far, we can easily evade them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:31.21,Default,JLF00,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:34.04,Default,JLF00,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, they are coming in from the path below.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:34.72,Default,JLF00,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.18,Note,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercury_fulminate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.18,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury (II) fulminate unit 2 activated. {bear - pls refer to http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercury_fulminate if you need to do a TL note =_=;}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.02,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,The four linked support structures on both sides are in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.71,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,Superconducting maglev style shrapnel cannon, energy confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.66,Default,Brit00,0000,0000,0000,,It's most likely an anti-Knightmare rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.17,Default,Brit00,0000,0000,0000,,Spread out and break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.30,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,Superconducting maglev style shrapnel cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.09,Default,OS/JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:54.68,Default,Brit00,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:58.95,Default,JLF03,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:06:59.96,Default,JLF04,0000,0000,0000,,With just one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.99,Default,JLF03,0000,0000,0000,,The Mercury (II) fulminate unit sure is useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.32,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Britannian pigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.50,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,All wiped out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:09.24,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has modified the Glasgow and placed something like a linear cannon on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.82,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that it's impossible to penetrate their defenses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.71,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.50,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Should we give into their demands and release the political criminals...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.33,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show weakness to the terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.30,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,However, Princess Euphemia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.16,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.45,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't have discovered that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.79,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,If they know that Princess Euphemia is among the hostages,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.37,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,they will definitely use that as leverage during the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:33.32,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Since Her Highness is just there to listen to the conference, her name isn't on the member list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.52,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.56,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,It will go well this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.23,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm not a guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:51.27,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Are we, the special envoys, not allowed to participate in the hostage rescue operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:56.09,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I made a request, but since our command structure is different, we're treated as irregulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.12,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.41,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,They can't leave the operation in the hands of an Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:06.59,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness Cornelia is a person that clearly distinguishes between Britannians and Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.75,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not enough for them to accept us, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:13.93,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, what purpose does the honorary Britannian system serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.93,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Are you her father? Shirley-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.81,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.56,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Over there around the driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.35,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's the box that was placed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.89,Default,Television,0000,0000,0000,,She was just sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:26.38,Default,Television,0000,0000,0000,,She's still just a student. And yet, the terrorists still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.17,Default,Television,0000,0000,0000,,This is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:30.36,Default,Television,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley... Is my daughter all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:33.16,Default,Television,0000,0000,0000,,That girl didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.61,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,An organization is necessary in order to fight against Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.13,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't leave things as they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.42,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Given Cornelia's personality, she will definitely ignore the hostage's presence, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.92,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then why hasn't she made a move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.35,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.76,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:57.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, there isn't any reason for them to release any Britannians.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.73,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,That... that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.80,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.77,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I distribute these to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:08.43,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're pretty cool, but we're a resistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:08.94,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.18,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We are not a resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.14,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What we are aiming for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.78,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To be the allies of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.75,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The special sniping platoon is in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.02,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,They are currently awaiting orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:27.39,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The commanders of each squadron are still conducting reconnaissance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:27.06,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,The students that are among the hostages are the people from the student council, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.53,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,The negotiations are still going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:30.96,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,I am a member of an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:34.55,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,I must place the ideals held by the organization before my own personal emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.18,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil-san, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.39,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:40.35,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.72,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the hostages are going to be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.26,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:43.98,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.86,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:55.54,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't receive any responses to our demands, we will make someone fly every thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:59.03,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that you can make a sincere effort on behalf of the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:01.80,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Killing someone just to show us they're serious. How barbaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:05.49,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,How about we proceed with the negotiations and request them to set the women and children free first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:05.80,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:10.11,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,If we give in, we'll only be acknowledging the terrorist's position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.48,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall we storm in by force?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:15.59,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We should only do that after we are sure about Princess Euphemia's safety, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.26,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.68,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-general, Zero has...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.85,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,We have received word from Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.02,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.54,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Car #3 was stolen by Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.19,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,What is the military doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.12,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that it was somehow stolen without them noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:32.96,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.69,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Then where is car #3 now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.03,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Right in the middle of the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.67,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's been confirmed that it's Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.71,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Should we snipe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.33,Default,???01,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.95,Default,???01,0000,0000,0000,,Apprehend him after you have surrounded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.31,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.39,Default,Kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean by "allies of justice"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.05,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.43,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,But we might get killed before we know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.71,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,The ones behind don't have any way to escape either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.12,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't we using that trailer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.62,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What would we do if our base is discovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:04.63,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that man, Zero, can be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.82,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said before that he's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.18,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll think of something if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:20.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like returning the big favor you did for me, but it's still too early to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.37,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If things go as I've planned, there isn't a need to use Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.28,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.08,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a member of the Japan Liberation Front?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.21,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you intend to provide assistance to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.41,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,However, our business comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.73,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Vengeance for my half brother, Clovis...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.87,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do that here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia, which will you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:47.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The dead Clovis, or Euphemia, who is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:49.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Good, it's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.57,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The first condition has been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You're still the same as ever, Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You have always pampered Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.11,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Emotions have hindered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:05.39,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I will save Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.35,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.76,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you are saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.42,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.10,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.84,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian Forces have contacted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.35,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, let Zero through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.26,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: Let Zero through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:35.13,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Will the Japan Liberation Front accept me as a fellow comrade, or will they treat me as a nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:41.76,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, they can't suppress this desire deep within their hearts that makes them yearn to see Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:49.42,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The prerequisite conditions to the operation have all been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.43,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Governor-general?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:57.56,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the arrival of Zero, the time before the next hostage is killed should be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.73,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,This is an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.92,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,We shall wipe them out, together with Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.28,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thanks for the appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.09,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,She said that we can launch Lancelot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:08.99,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.18,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,She said that you are to enter from the tunnel and head straight towards the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.96,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Llyod-san! Doesn't that mean they're telling us to act as bait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:19.93,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It seems like her special unit will break through during the confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.16,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,"Seems"?! Such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:21.81,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.65,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it. Please let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.91,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's possible to save everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:30.62,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,If Lancelot and I are required now, I should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.92,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that means acting as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:47.02,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kururugi, I shall now brief you on the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.35,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,According to the surveillance devices,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:52.97,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,the hostages are held near the middle tower, inside a food storage compartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:58.60,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Guided Weapon Z01 Lancelot shall use the lifeline tunnel and move towards the hotel basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:02.38,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Once near, you will destroy the foundation block and sink the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:06.02,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take an estimated eight minutes before the place where the hostages are becomes submerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:09.70,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,While the hostages are being saved, the elimination of the terrorists will be handled by another unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.40,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Now, in order to destroy the foundation, the VARIS will be employed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.87,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-material level 3 has been loaded into the Impact Rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:20.12,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is those people lying inside the tunnel ready to ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:25.26,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot's evasion rate is only 47.8% becase the area is constricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.73,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.60,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:32.22,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Come back when necessary. You can't afford to damage Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.76,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,"When necessary"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.64,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.06,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:42.42,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun, I'm going with the President and Nina to Kawaguchiko this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.23,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:46.00,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have work that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:49.28,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It can't be helped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:54.45,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks a lot. I'm really glad that you invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.19,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,12 minutes before the operation starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.08,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.15,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:04.46,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.96,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven?! We're Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.30,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,We understand, so stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.72,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Take your words back! We aren't called Elevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.54,Default,Millay,0000,0000,0000,,We take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.06,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.79,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here! I'll teach you all a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:20.78,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.89,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.90,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.26,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.48,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:31.86,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you, bitch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.86,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to your leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:36.24,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.08,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do this, Vice Governor-general!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:42.54,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I am the third princess of Britannia, Euphemia vie Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.31,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.59,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.51,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.79,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any intentions of allying with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.80,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Show us your face then, Zero. Isn't this rude of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:57.90,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.39,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is something I want to ask before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:04.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to achieve with these actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:09.21,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious. I want to announce to the world that the Japanese are still alive. {bear- That's it? o_O}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.23,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.11,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:14.61,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are old timers and can no longer be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.27,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.78,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.58,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,MA Boost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.12,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.14,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Reaction confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:28.85,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,One enemy Knightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:29.78,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,Acceleration rate is faster than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:30.64,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:31.67,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.25,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,Superconducting maglev style shrapnel cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.00,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.06,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.15,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he didn't intend to be bait and wants to finish them off instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.98,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought the hostage as reported to the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.16,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,She calls herself Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:02.25,Default,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, I have nothing left to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.43,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.29,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.51,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.02,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.18,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel and the rest have committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.14,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They realized how meaningless their actions are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.73,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Did you stand up in order to save the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You're still the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:30.35,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.01,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What? The Knightmare from the special envoy has...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:33.91,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.83,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,He can break through if he keeps this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.16,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Should I expect that of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:43.04,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I can still handle this level of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.10,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,It broke through the fifth volley!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.36,Default,JLF01,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelieveable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.49,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.66,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,Spread the cannons on the four linked support structures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:53.30,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,We must defend this place even to our deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.95,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil-san, I'm going to use the VARIS here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.05,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.49,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,My time to act is getting shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.89,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,I have long braced myself for the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.27,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:17.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that you have been appointed as Vice Governor-general, Your Highness Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.51,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be happy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Clovis is dead, since I've killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.67,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He was begging me for his life till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.61,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,With that mouth that ordered the murder of the Elevens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.74,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Was that why you killed my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:35.54,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.87,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Because that man was a child of the Imperial Emperor of Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:39.87,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.08,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.72,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You are one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:46.30,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on maximum power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.13,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if the barrel melts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.61,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,We must stop the interception no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.10,Default,JLF02,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:07.95,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,That Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.64,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,He did it? Gilford!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.01,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.01,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The white armor from back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:37.90,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:39.78,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:41.99,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Lieutenant Kururugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.74,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,How's camera #3?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.80,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Was it taken by Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.29,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm hoping there's some reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.29,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.84,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that your intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.10,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,To make use of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.42,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.26,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:19.79,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... {bear - If you're going to go Cloud on us, please do everyone a favor and omnislash Lelouch's daddy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.69,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.28,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:31.30,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That's... Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:34.67,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To all Britannians, there's no need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:38.38,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The hostages that were held in the hotel have all been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:41.04,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall return them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.09,Default,Suzuka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.72,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.89,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,A shameless lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:51.06,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,That only means  they will become hostages once again if we act against you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,People!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fear us or seek us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.82,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We are... the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.34,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,A knight order?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:06.35,Default,Llyod,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather ironic hearing terrorists calling themselves knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:11.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Order of the Black Knights, are allies of all those who hold no weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:15.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Be it Elevens or Britannians.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:22.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese Liberation Front used underhanded tactics, used Britannian civilians as hostages, and killed them in cold blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was a meaningless action.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we have punished them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.71,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you should keep relaying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:31.77,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.88,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.07,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Clovis, the previous Governor-general, was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:39.16,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He massacred Elevens who possessed no weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:45.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to see these kinds of cruel acts, which is why I punished him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.65,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wish to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:51.87,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, the act of the strong completely and utterly killing the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:52.99,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:57.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who are prepared to be killed should be allowed to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:03.46,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,When those with power attack those without, we will appear once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.76,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how great the power of the enemy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:10.60,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Allies... of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:13.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Those with power...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:15.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:17.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Those without power...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:18.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Seek us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:24.25,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The world shall be judged by us, the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:57.24,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.59,0:24:00.62,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have been wearing a mask ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:02.27,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A fake name...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.83,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A fake record...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:07.43,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But I have obtained two powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:09.75,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Geass and the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:12.60,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going just as I planned.
